claim: Whoopi Goldberg is of sub-Saharan African descent.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Dumas and Louverture  (  appointed a general-in-chief in 1797  )  were the two highest-ranking officers of sub-Saharan African descent in the Western world until 1975 , when `` Chappie '' James achieved the equivalent rank of four-star general in the United States Air Force .
